533
00:41:54,160 --> 00:41:57,520
I feel very sorry and embarrassed to Detective Jang,

534
00:41:57,520 --> 00:42:01,520
but you were the one who hugged me,

535
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:03,720
so I felt comforted and

536
